{"attributes":{"description":"Where turn latency goes -- stage breakdown of end-to-end request timing (90d default). STALE SIGNAL, flagged prominently: request_trace (the only Lens-queryable source for per-stage duration -- the alternative event_type:request_timing exists but its phase detail is mapped as ES type:nested, which standard Lens aggregations cannot reach) stopped emitting on 2026-06-07, 24+ days before this build. No replacement telemetry has been found. The original dashboard was also independently broken: panelsJSON referenced two panels (rt-avg-by-phase, rt-phase-table) with no matching visualization objects in the committed file, a top-level dashboard filter locked every panel to phase.keyword:llm_call:router (a value that does not exist in this schema), and the one fully-defined panel queried a total_duration_ms field that has zero documents under event_type:request_timing (the correct field lives on request_trace instead). All three original panels are replaced here with Lens objects built against the verified-live request_trace/phases_summary schema.","kibanaSavedObjectMeta":{"searchSourceJSON":"{\"query\":{\"language\":\"kuery\",\"query\":\"\"},\"filter\":[]}"},"optionsJSON":"{\"hidePanelTitles\":false,\"useMargins\":true}","panelsJSON":"[{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-1\",\"w\":48,\"x\":0,\"y\":0},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-1\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_0\",\"title\":\"Avg duration by stage\",\"type\":\"lens\",\"version\":\"8.9.0\"},{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-2\",\"w\":24,\"x\":0,\"y\":15},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-2\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_1\",\"title\":\"Total request duration over time\",\"type\":\"lens\",\"version\":\"8.9.0\"},{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-3\",\"w\":24,\"x\":24,\"y\":15},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-3\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_2\",\"title\":\"Request volume over time\",\"type\":\"le